short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Places Near Me replaces your new tab with quick access to Nearby Places & sponsored web search.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Installation of this extension will configure your New Tab Page to Places Near Me with Web Search, Time & Date, & Shortcuts. Places Near Me extension is all you need to start browsing with quick search for Places Nearby.

To get started, simply click "Places Near Me" on your new Tab Page & Search Any Place. Example: Type "Eye Doctor" & our system will show all Eye Doctor's near your location.

Permissions we request:

New Tab:
This permission allows the extension to replace the page you see when opening a new tab

Privacy Policy: https://placesnearme.org/pages/privacy.html
EULA: https://placesnearme.org/pages/eula.html

Uninstall Instructions: 
https://placesnearme.org/uninstall.html
